===============================================================================
[ Description ]

Procedural style

  finfo_set_flags(finfo $finfo, int $flags): true~

Object-oriented style

  public finfo::set_flags(int $flags): true~

This function sets various Fileinfo options. Options can be set also directly
in |finfo_open| or other Fileinfo functions.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{finfo}

  An finfo instance, returned by |finfo_open|.

{flags}

  One or disjunction of more Fileinfo constants.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

Always returns true.

